Package person

Class Faculty

java.lang.Object
person.Faculty
public class Faculty extends Object
The Faculty class holds information about a faculty member. - first name: first name of the student - last name: last name of the student - suid: Seattle U identification number - status: the status of the faculty (see PersonStatus enum) - faculty type: the type of faculty (see FacultyType enum) - office: includes building (i.e. BANN) and room number (i.e 504) - email: the school (i.e. SU) email address
